  <description>This measure updates the object representing the cold water temperatures delivered by underground water main pipes to the building. Water mains temperatures are a function of outdoor climate conditions and vary with time of year. No user arguments are required, as mains temperature is calculated based on information in the weather file.</description>
  <modeler_description>The measure will update the OS:Site:WaterMainsTemperature object. The object is currently configured to use the correlation method, but should be updated to a daily schedule to avoid issues with simulations in the southern hemisphere. </modeler_description>
